Sentencas: Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) is an interesting material for high temperature oxygen permeation membranes and solid oxide fuel cell cathodes, applications for which oxygen transport properties are crucial.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion in dense Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ films

Sentencas: Here oxygen isotope exchange is performed on dense BSCF films prepared by pulsed laser deposition on MgO single crystal substrates.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion in dense Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ films

Sentencas: The oxygen isotope profile is analyzed by secondary ion mass spectrometry to extract tracer diffusion coefficients D-* and effective surface exchange constants k(*).
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion in dense Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ films

Sentencas: Tracer diffusion has a low activation energy of 0.5 eV. At moderate temperatures, the related oxygen vacancy diffusion coefficient D-VO is significantly larger than that for (La,Sr)(Fe,Co)O3-delta perovskites.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion in dense Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ films
